    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> to the dish and cook for 15-20 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until the meatballs are cooked through and the sauce has thickened to a ragù-like consistency</p>",
